    "gp_section_568615017750987646": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "8fb9917b2a8588c513e1458c9a3b55fe3d56d6c55167980177dd446772546fe9_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-E0zj8IYQ_text": "<p>One night I couldn’t sleep (again) and was aimlessly scrolling my phone.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>Then I saw a headline that stopped me cold.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It turns out, <strong>the thing no one talks about is what’s actually happening to your spine and hips when you sleep on your side.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When I came across the term <strong>“Misalignment Lock”</strong>, something clicked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s the position your body naturally shifts into when sleeping on your side - where your top leg pulls your spine out of alignment, rotates your hips, and slowly compresses the sciatic nerve.</p>",
        "gg-kUwKbkU6_text": "<p>~ Lisa M., 47. Verified Customer</p>",
        "gg2Aet_zgzl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3017b1b0-2b34-4229-a09f-5499df679f31.jpg",
        "gg2sPjx9SWf_text": "<p>~ Susan W., 78. Verified Customer</p>",
        "gg4UiviMG9p_text": "Alignment Pillow",
        "gg6sZSk6gMV_text": "<p>I still woke up once or twice, but when I stood up that morning, something was… easier.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>There wasn’t that usual tightness that made me pause at the edge of the bed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>My back didn’t feel locked up.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I walked to the bathroom without wincing or bracing myself.</p>",
        "gg6zqppMkks_text": "<p>\"For years, I struggled with chronic hip tightness and <strong>lower back pain from my desk job</strong>. I’ve tried physical therapy, massage, and other support devices, but nothing gave me lasting relief—until now. <strong>After using the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow nightly, my hip pain has almost completely disappeared</strong>, and my sleep quality has improved. This device has truly improved my quality of life.\"</p>",
        "gg7Oecj-hwj_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/980684b3ff09432ebd0d254edac64742.mp4",
        "gg7Oecj-hwj_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg7Oecj-hwj_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg7XL8mL6AC_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Pillow fixed something I didn’t even know was broken.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>And <strong>it gave me back my mornings, my sleep, my energy</strong> - and honestly, my love for living life.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I’ve since bought a second one for travel.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Last time I ordered, <strong>there was very limited stock</strong> so I’d check and see if they’re still available.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If they are, I highly recommend buying a few pillows at least!&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You don’t have to keep on dragging through life deprived of genuine recovery.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You can change all of that today. <strong>Give this a try and get RID of the pain. You can thank me later.&nbsp;</strong></p>",
        "gg7nt4zF8jQ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1bc2ab13-1d13-401a-9d7e-342fee6d543e.png",
        "gg912yBeZeE_text": "The Real Root Cause Of My Back And Hip Pain&nbsp;",
        "gg9XyAbrxUC_text": "<p>~ Robert T., 61. Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggAbXBpGJek_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-52612e9e-33fb-4f8a-9400-21eb731ee9e3.png",
        "ggAkZDP2hHW_text": "<p>It arrived just a few days later - neatly packaged in a sturdy travel bag.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>That first night, I followed the simple instructions, placed the pillow between my legs, and slid the strap around my thigh.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It felt secure… supportive… and oddly comforting.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I didn’t expect much.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>But what happened next truly shocked me…</strong></p>",
        "ggAkz1jQVJC_text": "Rated 4.8/5 | 10,674+ Customers",
        "ggC1S73nPH7_text": "It is your spinal alignment during sleep.",
        "ggCrFeXtw36_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cb5f87ef-bbf9-40fa-a100-141946a4fb73.png",
        "ggCrJm6zHQy_label": "<p>Night 1:</p>",
        "ggHHLOP0hrT_text": "<p>\"I bought the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow for myself and one for my husband. We both use it every evening to relax before bed. <strong>It gently aligns our hips and relieves so much of the day’s tension.</strong> We’ve both been sleeping better and waking up without the usual stiffness. It’s honestly one of the <strong>best wellness purchases</strong> we’ve made in years.\"</p>",
        "ggIcKZq2dLN_text": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> Offer Not Available on Amazon Or eBay</p>",
        "ggJKT2WFLrE_label": "<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>",
        "ggJtxi2zxja_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-017cd110-db95-4d35-9a9d-6a7e7358522c.png",
        "ggK80D5UKCs_label": "<p>Check Availability</p>",
        "ggKey2KlyRL_text": "<p>At 56 years old, I never thought <strong>I’d be nervous to go to sleep</strong>.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But for the last 6 months, that’s exactly how it felt…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Every night, I’d lay down on my side like I always had - only to wake up hours later <strong>with burning pain in my hip</strong>, a stiff lower back, and shooting <strong>cramps down my leg</strong>.</p>",
        "ggLGevyOt7I_text": "Recommended",
        "ggM1bz3-9Al_text": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> Offer Not Available on Amazon Or eBay</p>",
        "ggMEF-gxYfx_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3017b1b0-2b34-4229-a09f-5499df679f31.jpg",
        "ggMEF-gxYfx_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0c27830a-6d21-40be-bd8f-316b0b6566cf.jpg",
        "ggNOTUZP6a9_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-42608570-7047-4b9c-8949-951fda186c1e.jpg",
        "ggNY422wyrh_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/69cf0b74040c49ae9ea571570077d30b.mp4",
        "ggNY422wyrh_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggNY422wyrh_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggOcyTXwgmg_text": "<p>It’s not something you can feel happening in the moment.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But hour after hour - night after night - it builds up.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Until suddenly <strong>you’re waking up with searing pain, lower back stiffness, or even signs of sciatica.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And here’s the kicker:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No mattress, back sleeping trick, or “regular” pillow fixes it</strong> - because they don’t actually support your top leg or correct your alignment while you sleep.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I couldn’t believe something so simple could be doing this much damage every night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And the video claimed <strong>there was a solution made specifically to stop it.</strong></p>",
        "ggOksm2tNyK_text": "<p>I raised three kids and walked five miles a day into my late 50s.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>And I never minded getting my hands dirty in the garden.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But suddenly, everything became harder:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I couldn’t stand for more than a few minutes</strong> without my hip flaring up.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Climbing the stairs felt like scaling a mountain.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I stopped walking with my neighbor in the mornings because I didn’t want to slow her down.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The worst part?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I started to feel like <strong>I was becoming dependent.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Like I was slowly watching my freedom - and my life - slip away.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Unable to enjoy what used to be my favourite activities.</p>",
        "ggPZYtTlG3x_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5177da4b-16e3-42fd-aa02-408bebb2c072.jpg",
        "ggPh6RhKUHj_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/495a61674ab34198b8fade42692accb2.mp4",
        "ggPh6RhKUHj_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggPh6RhKUHj_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggQ0l5ooEf9_text": "My Life Had Become a Never Ending Nightmare",
        "ggQLRUYPLjq_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-53bcc618-51d5-4b46-b181-676c4ef5e692.jpg",
        "ggRQo6qLzDv_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5177da4b-16e3-42fd-aa02-408bebb2c072.jpg",
        "ggRQo6qLzDv_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-59d65c5d-2422-44bf-9deb-ddd38083c961.jpg",
        "ggSRFFy-Soc_customText": "Rachel M. |",
        "ggTQtEIPwIR_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/98c43a8309fb4182a28c49a4a78091fb.mp4",
        "ggTQtEIPwIR_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggTQtEIPwIR_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggV0S4I6-28_text": "<p>\"I originally bought the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow for my daughter who works long hours at a computer and <strong>constantly complains of hip pain.</strong> After seeing how much it helped her, I ordered one for myself too. We both feel a noticeable difference after using it for just a few minutes each night. <strong>It’s easy to use, comfortable, and works like a charm.</strong>\"</p>",
        "ggVDDAQD4fA_label": "<p>Night 3:</p>",
        "ggVWTdgbm0H_text": "My Honest Experience After 14 Nights Of Sleep",
        "ggX4_f5toJx_text": "<p>Without invasive treatments, expensive physical therapy, or relying on harmful pills</p>",
        "ggXgtBAVWj3_text": "I Tried Everything You’re “Supposed” to Try… Or So I Thought",
        "ggYQWWuZDAe_label": "<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>",
        "ggYRxDJCJyx_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b6c4c810-edd0-48eb-86d1-73a91578b8bd.jpg",
        "ggYRxDJCJyx_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-860d0c0d-ac87-496c-9fa5-acf0550939ec.jpg",
        "ggYkMEDBO5U_text": "<p>~ Mark R., 43. Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggYvn-FlP0E_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ce79c43c-84ac-49ca-9a90-0127d408d66b.png",
        "ggefRUrDU56_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9d23f710552647f9843288c369b8ceae.mp4",
        "ggefRUrDU56_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggefRUrDU56_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggf3QwxbIIB_text": "<p>At first, I chalked it up to aging…<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But when the pain started waking me up every 2 hours…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And I needed my husband's help getting out of bed in the morning…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I knew something was completely wrong...</strong></p>",
        "ggfdmR4CCmf_text": "<p>\"I’ve been using the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow for <strong>about 20 minutes each evening before bed</strong>, and I can’t believe how much tension it releases from my hips and lower back. <strong>I feel so relaxed afterward</strong> that I often drift off right away. It’s also starting to help with my morning stiffness. Definitely recommend if you're dealing with hip strain from sitting all day.\"</p>",
        "gghL19RzZ1S_text": "<p>My first thought was that my mattress was too old.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>So I bought a brand-new one - medium-firm, memory foam, highly rated.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No change.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Then I tried stretching before bed. Foam rolling. Heating pads.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Even physical therapy, twice a week for two months.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The therapist told me it was “normal wear and tear.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They gave me some exercises and sent me on my way.</p>",
        "ggi7Yc08Xs8_text": "<p>I realized I hadn’t needed help getting out of bed all week.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>My balance was better. My movements felt more fluid.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Even my posture while standing seemed to have improved.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I told my husband, “I think this thing is actually working.”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>He smiled and said, “You’ve been sleeping through the night. I noticed.”</p>",
        "ggiCbF4bELi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1f6bb606-4269-4f4d-90c8-343e72ac1334.png",
        "ggiIJe69Rjo_text": "I Ordered My Own SmoothSpine Pillow Right Then And There",
        "ggiKerermPT_text": "<p>I walked the full loop around our neighborhood, twice, without that sharp pain that used to show up halfway through.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>I was doing things I hadn’t done in months:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Gardening for longer periods, shopping without needing to lean on the cart, and even rode in the car for 3 hours to visit my daughter, pain-free.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I felt more like myself again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>And all I had done was support my spine the right way while I slept.</strong></p>",
        "ggkWcDnYiSS_childItem_0": "<p>Alleviate Hip &amp; Lower Back Pain</p>",
        "ggkWcDnYiSS_childItem_1": "<p>Enhance Circulation &amp; Reduce Numbness</p>",
        "ggkWcDnYiSS_childItem_2": "<p>Promote Deeper, Restful Sleep</p>",
        "ggl6IFgAKrk_text": "<p>The video introduced a product called the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow - and right away, I could tell <strong>this wasn’t like anything I had tried.</strong>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>It didn’t look like a regular leg pillow.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It was contoured, structured, and <strong>had a soft, built-in strap</strong> that keeps it from shifting during the night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But what really caught my attention was how it worked…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The SmoothSpine Pillow uses something called: <strong>“Active Spine Realignment™”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A breakthrough support system <strong>developed by physiotherapists that corrects your sleep posture</strong>, stabilizes your hips, and keeps your spine perfectly aligned while you sleep on your side.</p>",
        "gglrQTX_5CM_text": "<p>If you’re anything like I was…<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>A side sleeper struggling with hip pain, lower back tension, or sciatic nerve flare-ups, and you’ve tried everything from fancy mattresses to stretches, but nothing sticks…</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Then please hear me when I say this:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It isn’t your mattress.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It isn’t your posture.</p>",
        "ggluNG2XzlS_text": "Not Your Ordinary Solution, Backed by Science",
        "ggm1CpQzLbl_text": "What Are People Saying About The SmoothSpine Pillow?",
        "ggm4JuZV5_W_text": "Final Thoughts (And Why I’m Writing This)",
        "ggmvc4TqCTS_text": "<p><strong>But each morning, I kept waking up in pain.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>And even worse, my mobility was getting worse day by day.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It terrified me.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I wasn’t ready to give up walking on my own.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I didn’t want to become one of those women who couldn’t go grocery shopping without help.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>And I refused to believe that this was “just part of getting older.”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So I went down the rabbit hole online, determined to find out what was really going on.</p>",
        "ggo15FepdP7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-17e6b322-d423-4a41-924b-6974cf0353c2.jpg",
        "ggokUTyl6M1_text": "<p>It sounded simple - and almost too good to be true.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>But the reviews?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Over 57,000 people had already used it, and the company was offering a 90-night money-back guarantee.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>At that point, I figured: what do I have to lose?</p>",
        "ggquE0QL4aq_label": "<p>Week 2:</p>",
        "ggrTon08aDs_text": "<p><strong>I noticed I was sleeping deeper.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>I didn’t wake up to shift positions like I usually did.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And for the first time in months, I didn’t reach for my morning pain cream.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I got dressed, made breakfast, and felt steady on my feet. That was a big deal for me.</p>",
        "ggrgqdVmkHg_label": "<p>Night 7:</p>",
        "ggsyXpBQsiT_text": "<p><strong>A Special Offer for Our Readers:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Claim Your SmoothSpine Pillow Now and <strong>SAVE 60% OFF</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>",
        "ggtFu4yDcD7_text": "By SmoothSpine™",
        "gguVSnF40Ak_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/c96e78e38c2e426f92e9edf4dda4bc87.mp4",
        "gguVSnF40Ak_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gguVSnF40Ak_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggvFTRsiEhf_text": "How I Finally Fixed My (Morning) Pain and ‘Regained’ 9 Hours of Sleep In <span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,228,0,0.77);\">Less Than 7 Days</span>",
        "ggxjdh2z0Xv_text": "<p>Take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>",
        "ggyUo6MBMWy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b39bd931-c2c0-476d-8578-3c2e153fd0d6.jpg",
        "ggz5GlnAJTM_text": "<p><strong>The 4 key changes it makes from night one:</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.</strong> <strong>Lifts your top leg</strong> so your hips stay level</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.</strong> <strong>Prevents your spine</strong> from twisting or rotating</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.</strong> Takes pressure off the sciatic nerve <strong>to stop that burning, shooting pain</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4. Stays in place all night</strong> - no shifting, sliding, or collapsing</p>",
        "ggzFfVcvDhC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b6c4c810-edd0-48eb-86d1-73a91578b8bd.jpg",
